1
00:00:15,640 --> 00:00:16,640
Oh, it's you two.

2
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:18,200
So you really are alive.

3
00:00:18,760 --> 00:00:20,239
Amitabha Buddha.

4
00:00:21,120 --> 00:00:23,039
Donor Chen, you bear the aspect of a great demon.

5
00:00:23,480 --> 00:00:25,039
Without the salvation of a Great Buddha,

6
00:00:25,360 --> 00:00:27,039
you would surely become a scourge
for a thousand years.

7
00:00:28,360 --> 00:00:29,360
Truth be told,

8
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:31,639
we came here to collect your corpse.

9
00:00:32,040 --> 00:00:32,719
Seems like

10
00:00:32,720 --> 00:00:34,079
we made a wasted trip.

11
00:00:36,200 --> 00:00:37,559
You risked danger to come for me.

12
00:00:37,920 --> 00:00:38,920
This debt of gratitude

13
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:40,000
I, Chen Nan, acknowledge.

14
00:00:42,760 --> 00:00:45,439
My dear Prince never fails to disappoint.

15
00:00:45,960 --> 00:00:47,119
Since Chen Nan is safe and sound,

16
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:48,199
you two...

17
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:50,079
wish to take your leave here?

18
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,520
Or...

19
00:00:52,040 --> 00:00:53,040
What?

20
00:00:53,360 --> 00:00:54,959
Need me to help you collect corpses too?

21
00:00:57,400 --> 00:01:00,559
Rumor has it Meng Ke'er challenged
the Successors of Righteousness and Evil

22
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:01,960
to a duel in the West.

23
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:03,639
It seems she was using these people

24
00:01:04,080 --> 00:01:05,759
to mask her true objective.

25
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:07,679
I, Chen Nan, survived this calamity.

26
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:10,119
Would you grant me this small courtesy

27
00:01:10,520 --> 00:01:11,520
to cease hostilities for now?

28
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:17,999
The Prince's face is naturally to be given.

29
00:01:18,320 --> 00:01:19,559
But next time...

30
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,159
who knows?

31
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:22,959
Brother Chen,

32
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,280
farewell.

33
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:27,599
Until we meet again.

34
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:29,439
Amitabha.

35
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:32,999
Where do you plan to go next?

36
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,479
Naturally, I shall return to the city
in glory

37
00:01:38,880 --> 00:01:40,639
and deliver a grand gift
to the Church of Light.

38
00:01:43,720 --> 00:01:44,319
Heard about it?

39
00:01:44,600 --> 00:01:46,079
That Easterner retrieved the Sacred Artifact.

40
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:49,439
Who would've thought there'd be
such a devout believer in the East?

41
00:01:58,720 --> 00:01:59,759
Hero!

42
00:01:59,960 --> 00:02:00,719
Hero!

43
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:01,800
Hero!

44
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:02,920
Hero!

45
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,000
Hero!

46
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,120
Hero!

47
00:02:07,440 --> 00:02:09,079
Young Master Chen's meritorious deeds

48
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:11,319
are engraved in the heart
of our Church of Light.

49
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,799
I, Chen Nan, dislike taking what others love.

50
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,280
My actions this time

51
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:22,319
were simply my duty.

52
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:28,879
If the Dark Church seeks revenge later,

53
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:31,999
you may present this medal at our church
to seek aid.

54
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,560
Hero!

55
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:35,639
Hero!

56
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:36,760
Hero!

57
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:37,800
Hero!

58
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:38,920
Hero!

59
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,000
Hero!

60
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:42,199
Then, I thank you in advance.

61
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:50,120
Hahaha!

62
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,919
The Church of Light is loudly
proclaiming your achievements.

63
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,239
You are thoroughly famous now.

64
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:56,200
However...

65
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,240
let me warn you,

66
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:59,639
those named "Light" are not necessarily bright.

67
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,519
I wonder if those charlatans

68
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,679
have noticed the
Divine Relic is missing?

69
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,959
But even if they haven't,

70
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:07,999
the Church of Light's actions

71
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:10,599
have completely enmified the
Dark Church against me.

72
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,599
Whether it's "raising bandits for leverage"

73
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:13,879
or maintaining

74
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,400
a balance of power,

75
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:18,479
they can all reap the benefits.

76
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:22,840
Brother Chen, do be careful.

77
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:24,679
The Dark Church has endured
for a thousand years...

78
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,240
It must have its strengths.

79
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:27,720
No matter.

80
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:30,319
Whether they "raise bandits for leverage"
or maintain parity,

81
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:31,799
chess players operating in the open

82
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:33,959
pose no real threat.

83
00:03:36,480 --> 00:03:37,759
Seems I needn't remind him.

84
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,399
Object Location Spell—

85
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,319
that's the Church of Light's
specialty after all.

86
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:42,840
Brother Kelly,

87
00:03:43,480 --> 00:03:44,480
I toast you.

88
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,839
Looks like you need a favor.

89
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:10,839
A small matter.

90
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:13,199
I plan to go to the Holy City of Baidan

91
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:15,239
to meet the highest hall
of the Church of Light.

92
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,439
Before I leave,

93
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:19,119
I'd like you to spread a message for me.

94
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:23,880
Chen'er...

95
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:25,879
You truly repay kindness
with kindness, and hate with hate.

96
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,000
What is this?

97
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:43,639
Hero and the Rose.

98
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:46,759
A love cursed by the gods.

99
00:04:47,200 --> 00:04:48,919
Trio of Fate.

100
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:49,759
Knight.

101
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:52,239
The perilous game between the Mage
and the Female Assassin.

102
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:54,959
Chen Nan, you bastard!

103
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:56,679
You've disturbed my Dao Heart so much.

104
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,360
Damn it!

105
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:17,239
He actually managed to kill
four peerless experts.

106
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:21,599
Why is his progress so godlike?

107
00:05:31,280 --> 00:05:32,319
I refuse to accept this!

108
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:34,879
I will close my seclusion right now
and break through.

109
00:05:35,320 --> 00:05:36,320
If I don't reach the Fifth Rank,

110
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,159
I swear I won't leave seclusion!

111
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:50,520
Brother Chen,

112
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:52,519
lend you my Unicorn temporarily.

113
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:54,200
Once you reach your destination,

114
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,199
it will return on its own.

115
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,760
Then, I thank you.

116
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,600
Have a safe journey.

117
00:06:01,624 --> 00:07:21,724
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

118
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,160
Father once said,

119
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:24,960
the path of the warrior

120
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:26,479
is not about closed-door training.

121
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,439
Cultivating martial arts
is tempering the heart.

122
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,999
A flash between life and death
is cultivation.

123
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:36,159
The mortal world of red dust
is also cultivation.

124
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,480
A warrior's Dao

125
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,879
first requires understanding
the human heart,

126
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,480
then learning martial skills.

127
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:43,559
Only then can the mental state
be perfect and round.

128
00:07:44,080 --> 00:07:45,119
Whole and without flaw.

129
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,240
Following successive great battles,

130
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:48,719
breaking through feels as natural

131
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:54,999
as water flowing to its level.

132
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:57,880
Fifth Rank Peerless.

133
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:03,640
Break!

134
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:13,519
This is the border region
of the four empires.

135
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:15,159
Originally a land of a hundred wars,

136
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,359
but due to the intervention
of the Church of Light,

137
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:18,920
it has gradually become peaceful.

138
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:20,400
Chen Nan,

139
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,159
why did that big con artist's relic

140
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:25,159
turn into a horn sprouting
from my head?

141
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:26,400
It's hideous!

142
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:27,039
Is it?

143
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:28,719
I think it looks rather cute.

144
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:30,599
This baby wants to be dashing,

145
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:31,959
not cute!

146
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,400
Hahaha!

147
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,320
Some petty thieves.

148
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,120
After traveling for so many days,

149
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:49,399
the Dark Church finally couldn't
hold back.

150
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:01,680
Strange.

151
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:03,359
Why do I sense on this man...

152
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:05,519
a breath of the same origin as myself?

153
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,200
You...

154
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:08,480
are Chen Nan?

155
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:09,879
Come.

156
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:11,199
Let me see

157
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:13,479
just how much the so-called
Number One of the Younger Generation

158
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,559
really weighs.

159
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:22,080
This aura...

160
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:28,760
Sky Severing Hand.

161
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:32,399
I thought it was just
a coincidence of names,

162
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:34,839
but it seems the legend is true.

163
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,600
Chen Nan,

164
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,359
you are a descendant of Chen Zhan.

165
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:39,640
You...

166
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:41,279
are a man returned from the dead.

167
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:42,719
This secret,

168
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:45,199
besides myself and the Nameless Demon,

169
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,519
should be known by no one.

170
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,080
I don't understand.

171
00:09:48,400 --> 00:09:49,400
You can quibble,

172
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:50,920
but techniques

173
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:52,080
cannot lie.

174
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:54,800
Baby Dragon,

175
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:55,840
stand guard.

176
00:09:56,160 --> 00:09:57,359
This man is connected
to my Chen family.

177
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,000
I'll handle him myself.

178
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:00,400
Listen well.

179
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:00,959
Chen Nan,

180
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,480
the one who kills you

181
00:10:02,640 --> 00:10:03,640
is Du Yu.

182
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:05,800
Du Yu.

183
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,199
Why do you know the secret arts
of my Chen family?

184
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:10,840
Before you die,

185
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:13,079
I will mercifully tell you.

186
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:20,720
Every technique you know,

187
00:10:21,040 --> 00:10:22,040
I know as well.

188
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:23,919
And I am only Fifth Rank.

189
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:25,640
Fifth Rank?

190
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,719
Didn't you know that two months ago,

191
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:30,319
I killed four Fifth Rank experts
in a single day?

192
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:33,840
Ridiculous.

193
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,240
After the Profound Art permeates
the body,

194
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:37,399
even a Fourth Rank can suppress
a Fifth Rank.

195
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:39,080
If it were me,

196
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,919
I could have annihilated
those four without a scratch.

197
00:10:43,880 --> 00:10:45,439
Unlike you, who was so battered.

198
00:10:48,560 --> 00:10:49,839
Your Profound Art True Qi...

199
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:51,319
it's actually multicolored?

200
00:10:54,640 --> 00:10:55,159
Pathetic.

201
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:56,600
Ridiculous.

202
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,479
My Du family has been inherited
for ten thousand years.

203
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:02,679
We are the emperors of the Eastern Lands'
cultivation world.

204
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:04,520
Today,

205
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:07,439
I shall rid you, the so-called
Number One of the Younger Generation.

206
00:11:07,680 --> 00:11:08,959
I will show the world

207
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:11,039
what a true Royal Family is.

208
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,279
Your legwork lacks refinement,

209
00:11:20,680 --> 00:11:21,680
your Qi circulation is sluggish.

210
00:11:22,400 --> 00:11:24,399
You even cultivated the Golden
Profound Art into a motley version.

211
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,279
This technique in your hands

212
00:11:26,680 --> 00:11:28,119
is a sheer waste of heavenly gifts.

213
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:37,080
This Profound Art

214
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:38,959
is only fit to be used by my Du family.

215
00:11:40,640 --> 00:11:41,640
You...

216
00:11:41,800 --> 00:11:42,800
are unworthy.

217
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:49,600
You say

218
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:50,960
I am unworthy?

219
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:04,960
Wha—!

220
00:12:12,920 --> 00:12:13,920
Impossible!

221
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:15,159
The silver

222
00:12:15,520 --> 00:12:16,239
and yellow True Qi of my clansmen

223
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:17,999
cannot even compare to mine.

224
00:12:18,400 --> 00:12:20,399
Yet you possess this chaotic, mixed Qi?

225
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:22,359
My clansmen are all...

226
00:12:22,560 --> 00:12:22,999
Very well.

227
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:24,000
Very well.

228
00:12:24,920 --> 00:12:26,239
You people are truly...

229
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,440
Damnable!

230
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:40,439
The Imperial Du Family?

231
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,919
What third-rate, backwater clan is that?

232
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,679
In the cultivation history
of the Eastern Continent,

233
00:12:45,160 --> 00:12:47,239
there has never been a great clan
surnamed Du.

234
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:48,359
Damn it!

235
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:50,239
If not for the Bloodline Curse,

236
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:51,639
my Du family would have long
since emerged into the world.

237
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:55,680
I understand now.

238
00:12:55,920 --> 00:12:56,920
What are you laughing at?

239
00:12:57,040 --> 00:12:57,719
Back then,

240
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:59,879
it must have been my Chen family
who imparted techniques to yours.

241
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:02,399
And granted you a corresponding mission.

242
00:13:02,920 --> 00:13:03,679
Otherwise,

243
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:05,759
why would we give our Profound Arts
to outsiders?

244
00:13:06,920 --> 00:13:09,639
Your Du lineage has served my Chen family
for many years.

245
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:11,479
and has been quite diligent.

246
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:14,359
Now, I shall transmit to you
the Upper Volume of the Profound Art.

247
00:13:14,640 --> 00:13:16,199
You must cultivate it with care.

248
00:13:16,880 --> 00:13:18,039
Thank you, My Lord!

249
00:13:18,400 --> 00:13:20,359
I require you to swear a
Bloodline Venomous Oath:

250
00:13:21,040 --> 00:13:22,040
After I depart,

251
00:13:22,640 --> 00:13:24,759
your lineage shall reside in seclusion
within the Mystic Realm.

252
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,000
You are forbidden to emerge.

253
00:13:26,800 --> 00:13:29,399
When ten thousand years have passed
and my son returns,

254
00:13:29,560 --> 00:13:30,679
you shall pledge allegiance to him.

255
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:31,559
At that time,

256
00:13:31,680 --> 00:13:34,479
he will naturally transmit
the Lower Volume to you.

257
00:13:35,400 --> 00:13:36,719
This lowly one has noted it well.

258
00:13:40,560 --> 00:13:41,560
In other words,

259
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:43,360
your family

260
00:13:43,640 --> 00:13:45,399
should have been servants
of my Chen family.

261
00:13:46,760 --> 00:13:48,599
But with the master absent,

262
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:51,039
the tail wags the dog,
and you've grown arrogant.

263
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:53,200
Impudent!

264
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:16,840
You...

265
00:14:17,400 --> 00:14:18,400
You are simply...

266
00:14:18,680 --> 00:14:19,719
You are not even Fourth Rank!

267
00:14:20,840 --> 00:14:22,199
Finally figured it out?

268
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:25,959
I only recently broke through.

269
00:14:27,160 --> 00:14:29,599
I originally intended to give
the Dark Church a surprise,

270
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:32,199
but the first to arrive

271
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:35,119
is a master-biting, wild dog.

272
00:14:49,640 --> 00:14:50,039
This...

273
00:14:50,560 --> 00:14:51,560
What sort of technique is this?

274
00:14:57,760 --> 00:14:59,719
A wicked slave biting its master—

275
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:01,359
I shall be the one to

276
00:15:02,160 --> 00:15:03,959
cleanse the family of this disgrace.

277
00:15:07,370 --> 00:15:12,036
[Dong Family — Located in the western Taiyin region, a land rich in divine sources, the Dong Family stands as a prominent ancient clan with immense heritage and strength; their lineage is deeply rooted, producing many powerful experts across generations, and their influence extends far and wide, making them one of the most formidable families in the region. Land of a Hundred Battles — A harsh and chaotic domain where conflicts never cease, filled with endless struggles and trials; only the strong can survive here, tempering themselves through constant battle to rise above others and carve out their own legend.]

